Super Grand Gourmet Wine Gift Basket
List.Description:
We filled this basket to the brim with an unparalleled selection of four delicious wines sure to impress the discerning palate: Pommery Brut Royal, Hess Collection Napa Valley Chardonnay, Sebastiani Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon and Fonseca Bin No. 27 Port. To this we added a collection of superb goodies and tied it up with a festive bow!

Wine Gift Basket Includes:

  • Pommery Brut Royal:
    This fine Champagne is a blend of 40 carefully selected crus from the Champagne region. It is made up of three grape varieties: Pinot Noir, Pinot Meunier, and about one-third Chardonnay. A composition that is light yet well-structured and full of charm.

  • Hess Collection Napa Valley Chardonnay:
    This Chardonnay includes subtle notes of vanilla bean and brioche which complement distinctive citrus aromas such as Clementine tangerine and lemon zest. Fermenting in stainless, as well as barrels, brings focus to the bright fruit characters of white nectarine, pear and green apple.

  • Sebastiani Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon:
    This Cabernet Sauvignon displays black tea and black cherry aromas complemented with coconut and mocha from the oak. The flavors in this wine emphasize black cherries, truffles, earth, and dust. The finish possesses enough tannin to support the abundant levels of fruit.

  • Fonseca Bin No. 27 Port:
    This Port was blended from reserve wines selected for their intense fruit character and depth of color. Its well-knit structure, rich full body, and luscious blackcurrant and cherry flavors, also evident in the nose, carry into an intense, lingering finish.

  • Woven Wicker Basket
  • Butter Cookies Dipped in Vanilla Butter 7 oz
  • Nunes Farms Pistachios 16 oz
  • Butter Toffee Pretzels 2 oz
  • Caramel Popcorn 8 oz
  • French Country Olive Mix 4.4 oz
  • Focaccia Crisps 8 oz
  • Lemon Almond Biscotti 6 oz
  • Sonoma Jacks Parmesan Peppercorn Cheese 4 oz
  • Dried Mixed Fruit 8 oz
  • Wild Smoked Salmon 2 oz
  • Godiva 19-piece Gold Ballotin 7.2 oz
  • Godiva Signature Biscuits 3.5 oz
  • Cracked Black Pepper Crackers 2.8 oz

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.
